Title: Work Order: The August Celestials II
Description:
Once your striped melons are ready to be picked, you'll need only to package them for pick-up.

A trainee from the Cradle of Chi-Ji will be along shortly to collect their order.
ObjectivesText: Harvest 8 Ripe Striped Melon plants and provide 40 Striped Melons for the August Celestials.
